video_title: Which feeling encourages growth: guilt or love? #podcast #lilnasx #jayshetty
transcript:
you can't guilt yourself into growth
it's impossible like you can't shame
yourself or embarrass yourself into
becoming better like when was the last
time you made someone feel guilty and
they were like yeah I'm going to be the
best person in the world now like it
doesn't work that way cliche as it is
like you know love is really the the
answer for that
